  "3035880": {
    "name": "恶魔细雨",
    "steam_appid": 3035880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras/2cd5526689449dce9626b40efd5e7d74.avif?t=1770562106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras_big/2cd5526689449dce9626b40efd5e7d74.avif?t=1770562106 width=800 height=371 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你所在的社区边界之外，一个未知的世界正等待着你和你忠实的伙伴。脚踩靴子，手持伞，天生渴望探索，这就是你开始这场冒险所需的一切！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras/77a1953380275adc246a89f03a602782.avif?t=1770562106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras_big/77a1953380275adc246a89f03a602782.avif?t=1770562106 width=800 height=408 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Devil’s Drizzle</i> 以可爱但令人不安的美学为特点，是一款通过一个天真孩子的视角讲述的 2D 平台冒险游戏。面对你的噩梦，征服黑暗，战斗毛茸茸的怪物，并在这片未被探索的土地上与古老的苏美尔恶魔对抗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras/9a17ac57b3ce877dfcefbc8ceb862c2a.avif?t=1770562106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras_big/9a17ac57b3ce877dfcefbc8ceb862c2a.avif?t=1770562106 width=800 height=425 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典平台机制与现代增强。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧凑的控制。跳跃、冲刺，并击败敌人，穿越神秘的环境。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态光照。使用神话护身符的闪电揭开黑暗中的隐藏秘密！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像素艺术图形。用精美的像素艺术重温经典游戏的魅力！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的景观。探索遥远的森林，深入苏美尔恶魔的肚腹，并在梦境世界中面对你的恐惧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态关卡与独特机制。飞翔在天空中，自由落体逃脱帕祖祖，解开谜题与敌人对战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss 战斗。面对死亡巨毛球，挑战邪恶伞，并打败可怕的帕祖祖！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复杂的对话与故事。应对不安情绪，反思你的存在，并揭示友谊的真正意义！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重结局。完成故事并揭示三个可能的结局！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras/79da5d6526b63d45f6ecbd68257206ba.avif?t=1770562106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras_big/79da5d6526b63d45f6ecbd68257206ba.avif?t=1770562106 width=800 height=371 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >手工制作的故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Devil’s Drizzle</i> 的世界通过才华横溢的创作者们的作品栩栩如生，采用手绘的 2D 插图和动画。每个你探索的新区域都有其独特的风格，充满了新的机制、敌人和富有意义的细节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入这场冒险！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你是经典游戏的粉丝，喜欢可爱却令人不安的美学，充满转折的剧情和影响深远的结局，那么 <i>Devil’s Drizzle</i> 是你下一个冒险的完美选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras/faedccd5e874207cd7e1f81e889fd55e.avif?t=1770562106\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035880/extras_big/faedccd5e874207cd7e1f81e889fd55e.avif?t=1770562106 width=800 height=631 /></span></p>",
